        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(center)"><placeName>Evansville</placeName>
                <date>Apl 8. 1861</date>—</p>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p>
                <placeName>Philadelphia Pa</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>D<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Sir!</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">It has been some time<lb/> since I had this pleasure, but it
                has<lb/> not been my fault, absence from home<lb/> and constant employment are the
                cau,<lb/>ses;— <del>but</del> and I hope you will par,<lb/>don me.— Enclosed I hand
                you a few<lb/> pages appertaining to <add>קהל</add> here, for pub,<lb/>lication in
                your valuable paper; which<lb/> I hope you will insert, but request you<lb/> at the
                same time to examine it, if you<lb/> find any mistakes please correct, I<lb/> am not
                a very good writer.— I am<lb/> very much pleased with the contem˶<lb/>plated changes
                of your paper.— If<lb/> any body is owing you here at this</p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p>place, please send me the bills<lb/> I will collect for you.— Please<lb/> send me
                bill of in your next fa,<lb/>vour of my own <sic>intebdness</sic>; which<lb/> I will
                promptly <sic>remitt</sic> you.—<lb/> As I have nothing else to
                com<add>m</add>uni,<lb/>cate at present; allow me to assure<lb/> you of the high
                    <del>esteem</del> esteem I entertain<lb/> and remain Respectfully<lb/>
                <sic>Truely</sic> yours</p>
            <p>
                <persName role="author">L. M. Plant</persName>
            </p>
            <p>Enclosed I hand you the right to<lb/> collect funds for the <add>קהל</add> for the
                    pur<lb/><sic>puse</sic> to erect synagogue; if you can do<lb/> any thing for
                her, it will be <sic>duely</sic><lb/> appreciated.</p>
            <p>
                <persName role="author">P.</persName>—</p>
        </body>
